Ports Layer:

```rust
#[derive(HexPort)]
trait TodoRepository: Repository<Todo> {
    fn find_active(&self) -> HexResult<Vec<Todo>>;
    fn find_completed(&self) -> HexResult<Vec<Todo>>;
}
